351  updateError = DM.Compile(true) ? updateError : "Compilation failed!";
352  }
353  break;
354  case FullUpdateAction.UpdateHardTestmerge:
355  updateError = Repo.Update(true);
356  if (updateError == null)
357  {
358  Repo.GenerateChangelog(out updateError);
359  if (updateError == null)
360  updateError = Repo.SynchronizePush();
361  updateError = Repo.MergePullRequest(testmergePR);
362  if (updateError == null)
363  {
364  Repo.GenerateChangelog(out updateError);
365  updateError = DM.Compile(true) ? updateError : "Compilation failed!";
366  }
367  }
368  break;
369  case FullUpdateAction.UpdateMerge:
370  updateError = Repo.Update(false);
371  if (updateError == null)
372  {
373  Repo.GenerateChangelog(out updateError);
374  if (updateError == null)
375  Repo.SynchronizePush(); //not an error 99% of the time if this fails, just a dirty tree
376  updateError = DM.Compile(true) ? updateError : "Compilation failed!";
377  }
378  break;
379  case FullUpdateAction.Reset:
380  updateError = Repo.Reset(true);
381  if (updateError == null)
382  {
383  Repo.GenerateChangelog(out updateError);
384  updateError = DM.Compile(true) ? updateError : "Compilation failed!";
385  }
386  break;
387  }
388  }
389  catch (Exception ex)
390  {
391  Program.ServiceDisconnectException(ex);
392  }
393  }
